    Closed --> [*]

    note right of Unconnected
        Socket created without connection.
        bind() can be called once before connect().
        setReceiveBufferSize() must be called before connect() for large TCP windows.
    end note

    note right of Connected
        Socket connected. Both input and output streams active.
        shutdownInput() and shutdownOutput() independently close stream halves.
    end note

    note right of Closed
        Terminal state. Once closed, socket cannot be reconnected or rebound.
        isBound() and isConnected() remain sticky (return true if previously set).
    end note
